Prerequisites for this is to have the ec2 instance terraformed 
from the repository demo_cicd master branch

Also you need to fork the repository demo_cicd to your github

https://github.com/ajoybharath/demo_cicd.git

A pipeline build for invoking terraform

1. New pipeline job is created

Source Code Management > Git

Repository URL

Pipeline

Definition > Pipeline script from SCM

SCM - Git > add repository

	Repositories > 	Repository URL

	Branches to build

			Branch Specifier (blank for 'any') (demo_tf in our case)

Script Path > will autopopulate

Save and Build

